      <h1>Frugality vs Investing: Why Both Matter and How to Balance Them</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Extreme frugality and aggressive investing are often pitted against each other. The optimal path combines both — but the balance shifts by life stage, income, and goals.</p>
      <span>By <strong>{author}</strong></span>
    </header>

